        "TileImage": "$($repository 6dfe141c-fa3b-422a-a28e-3ce2af1069ed).Image",
        "Description": "An apricot—harmless, insignificant, and never meant to kill.\nBut today, that assumption no longer holds.\n\nYour targets are five individuals, each dressed in distinct attire.\nThough they share the same space, they stand apart—defined by their differences, not their similarities.\n\nYour objective is simple.\nEliminate all five targets using nothing but a “harmless” piece of fruit.\n\nTurn the impossible into reality.",
